snippet.title: Tailspin! - Videogame Trailer
snippet.description:
Ludum Dare Page : https://ldjam.com/events/ludum-dare/48/tailspin

Team Bugulon's sixth videogame, made for the Ludum Dare 48 Jam 2021.

Play as a treasure seeking canary and drill through 4 unique worlds of action packed platforming. Can you survive the infested depths below and attain everlasting glory? 

You can play it here : https://team-bugulon.itch.io/tailspin

Tailspin! OST : https://mistajub.bandcamp.com/album/tailspin

Video edited by Oroshibu :)
